    <user>dimstar_suse</user>
    <comment>Security re-vendor: golang.org/x/net 0.55.0 + golang.org/x/crypto 0.52.0
Fixes bsc#1265736, bsc#1266575, bsc#1267120, bsc#1266151. No code changes:
vendored dependency refresh only, upstream tag 1.8.4 unchanged.</comment>
